## Exemplos de Cenários

### Cenário 1 — Controller protegido com JWT

```csharp
[ApiVersion("1.0")]
[Authorize]  // ← protege todos os endpoints
public class OrdersController(IMediator mediator) : BaseApiController
{
    [HttpGet]
    [Authorize(Roles = "Admin,Manager")]  // ← role específica
    public async Task<IActionResult> GetAll(CancellationToken ct)
        => HandleResult(await mediator.Send(new GetOrdersQuery(), ct));
}
```

### Cenário 2 — Resposta de paginação com headers

```csharp
[HttpGet]
public async Task<IActionResult> GetAll([FromQuery] GetProductsPagedQuery query, CancellationToken ct)
{
    var result = await mediator.Send(query, ct);
    if (result.IsFailure) return HandleResult(result);

    // Adiciona headers de paginação
    Response.Headers["X-Total-Count"] = result.Value.Total.ToString();
    Response.Headers["X-Total-Pages"] = result.Value.TotalPages.ToString();

    return Ok(result.Value);
}
```

